  "texts": [
    "Below we provide classroom activity ideas that incorporate adversarial attacks.",
    "Comparative Prompt Analysis Teachers can begin by introducing students to AI-generated content, asking them to compare different prompt formulations.",
    "For example, students can compare two distinct prompts in which ChatGPT is asked to either \"confirm\" a fact or determine whether a statement is \"true or false\".",
    "Students will analyze the differences in how ChatGPT approaches these tasks and discuss why certain responses may vary based on the wording of the prompt.",
    "This activity can help students understand how the phrasing of a question can influence AI outputs, while emphasizing the importance of clarity in scientific inquiry."
  ],
